CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 31, 1962, pg. 14, reads: "Sunday School Committee - The Rodman Street Sunday School Committee (left to right, seated): M. E. Nelson, D. Updyke, Nathan May, Lena Yuille, Rev. G. L. Bowick, Mabel Stewart and Sedonia Mack. Standing: L. Yuille, L. Gaskin, L. Calloway, L. Drake Sr. and Ethel Calloway. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Rodman Street Church Sunday School Committee, seated from left: M. E. Nelson, D. Updyke, Nathan May, Lena Yuille, Rev. G. L. Bowick, Mabel Stewart, Sedonia Mack; standing: L. Yuille, L. Gaskin, L. Calloway, L. Drake Sr., and Ethel Calloway
